 days #n of the server opening. Make sure to claim them in time. #r3. All Agents who participate in the open beta will get 300 Hero Coins. #r4. This rebate amount will not be included as part of top-up events after the open beta. #r4. Paid items deleted after the game wipe will be refunded as Hero Coins for compensation. #r5. When claiming a reward, Hero Coins activated by the Monthly Card will pop-up first, then the top-up rebate reward will pop-up. #r6. Top-up rebate reward claim time: 12/3/2020ΓÇöΓ\128\1483/2/2021.",
